\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f0\fs22\lang9 Bootstrap Spinners\par
Spinner is also called a loading indicator. It is used to display/indicate the loading state of our projects. Bootstrap uses a .spinner class to create a Spinner.\par
\par
We use the below syntax to create a Spinner in Bootstrap -\par
\par
<div class = "spinner-border"> </div>  \par
Types of Spinners\par
There are the following types of spinners that we create using Bootstrap -\par
\par
1. Border Spinner\par
Border Spinner is used for lightweight indicators.\par
\par
Pause\par
\par
Unmute\par
