\par
Fullscreen\par
\par
We use the below syntax to create a Border Spinner in Bootstrap -\par
\par
Syntax:\par
\par
<div class = "spinner-border" role = "status">  \par
  <span class = "sr-only">Loading...</span>  \par
</div>  \par
